<title>CANADA: ISG Technologies opposes Quorum board.</title>
<headline>ISG Technologies opposes Quorum board.</headline>
<dateline>TORONTO 1996-12-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>ISG Technologies Inc issued a letter to its shareholders on Thursday asking them to vote for an ISG-supported slate of directors and to oppose a list proposed by Quorum Growth Inc.</p>
<p>ISG said that Quorum Growth, which holds seven percent of ISG's stock, is trying to gain control of ISG by electing a seven-member board, five of whom are directors or officers of Quorum or Quorum-related companies.</p>
<p>ISG will hold its annual meeting on December 23.</p>
<p>((Reuters Toronto Bureau (416) 941-8100))</p>
